            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/9f0a66bf42729524/text/000004482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9f0a66bf42729524-9b89d6 twpub-9f0a66bf42729524-054be7 twpub-9f0a66bf42729524-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"c15\"><div class=\"c2\">Please check the Project Gutenberg web pages for current donation methods and addresses. Donations are accepted in a number of other ways including checks, online payments and credit card donations. To donate, please visit: www.gutenberg.org/donate</div></div></div>"
